data.description: Nestled on a picturesque .72-acre lot, graced with sublime tree-lined surroundings is this single level 1,655 SqFt home. As you approach the property, you will be greeted by a circular driveway, adding both convenience and charm to the entrance. A handy toolshed stands nearby, providing practical storage space, while the property's mature trees ensure a sense of privacy and natural tranquility.Upon entering the house, you will find the living room that opens into a welcoming step-down family room. The dining area seamlessly connects to both the kitchen and the family room, making it an ideal setup for gatherings and family meals. The kitchen features garden windows, a pantry for your storage needs, and ample cabinetry to accommodate all your kitchen essentials.The primary bedroom boasts its own private bath with a convenient step-in shower. Outside, a large carport and a double garage complete with workbenches offers a fantastic space for DIY projects and hobbies. Above the garage, you will discover two bonus rooms that can be utilized as home offices, additional storage, or a variety of other purposes.The backyard provides a secure area for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the peaceful ambiance of the property. With plenty of space both indoors and outdoors, this residence is perfect for hobbyists and those seeking a dedicated workshop area. Additionally, its proximity to the Munsel Lake boat dock, just across the street, makes it an ideal location for boating and water enthusiasts.
